{"tid":2221208,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【警署掟汽油彈】18歲勇武火魔承認「貪玩」　冀示威者不要仿效他","createTime":"2020-09-28T08:03:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T05:08:25.000Z","uid":10199,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"39c99fb49733df644a00c1d4fa520575eb31177b","tid":2221208,"uid":10199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T08:03:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image2.stheadline.com/f/874p0/0x0/100/hd/e1921d14c6dab54dd3252bc5aaa2f133/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200928/_2020092811130886906.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage2.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F874p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fhd%2Fe1921d14c6dab54dd3252bc5aaa2f133%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200928%2F_2020092811130886906.jpg&h=2f886764&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n去年輟學中四的18歲男學生陳俊輝，本年初夥同兩名黑衣人向葵涌警署投擲汽油彈導致車閘起火，並聲稱因為「貪玩」而在工業大廈單位內貯存11支汽油彈和原材料等。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n他早前承認一項縱火罪及一項管有物品意圖摧毀財產罪。區域法院法官胡雅文判處他入獄3年10個月。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n被告透過辯方律師求情指，他在傳媒的渲染下犯案，事後已知道自己是一名壞榜樣，冀其他示威者不要仿效他。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n精神科專家確認他患上過度活躍症，由於被告犯案時僅17歲，法庭除了監禁外，仍有多項判刑選擇。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1884080/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-18%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E7%94%9F%E5%90%91%E8%91%B5%E6%B6%8C%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%B2%E6%8E%9F%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88%E7%AD%89-%E5%9B%9A3%E5%B9%B410%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1884080%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-18%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%2590%2591%25E8%2591%25B5%25E6%25B6%258C%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E6%258E%259F%25E6%25B1%25BD%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E5%25BD%2588%25E7%25AD%2589-%25E5%259B%259A3%25E5%25B9%25B410%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588&d=Wx0cKZaQlto0GELw8F4hIZHrfcRVF4fwerrMnmH2A0w%3D&h=b722f0be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1884080%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%2